CLIP-enhanced multimodal baselines

This folder contains scripts for the CLIP-related parts of the manuscript:

- `clipscore.py` computes image-text semantic alignment scores for generated
  or human-written captions.
- `clip_human_gpt4omini.py` fine-tunes CLIP-based image-text classifiers with
  GPT-4o-mini or human descriptions using the manuscript's contrastive +
  classification objective, then exports OOF predictions for comparison with
  the image-only ViT baseline and DamageArbiter.

The manuscript compares CLIP-LLM and CLIP-Human settings, then uses the CLIP-LLM
OOF predictions as one input to the final arbitration stage.
